 <body ><br><h1 class="pHead1" >
assert_win_change
</h1>    
<a name="wp3719828"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that the value of a specified expression changes in a specified window between a start event and an end event.  </p>    <div align="left" class="tbl">
